03:11.797 --> 03:13.277
[Engine starts]

03:14.517 --> 03:18.018
<i>[Male sings] ♪ I saddled
up and away I did go ♪</i>

03:18.324 --> 03:25.176
<i>♪ riding alone in the dark ♪</i>

03:25.574 --> 03:28.076
<i>♪ maybe tomorrow</i>
<i>a bullet may find me ♪</i>

03:28.094 --> 03:32.097
<i>♪ tonight nothing's worse</i>
<i>than this pain in my heart ♪</i>

03:32.131 --> 03:37.418
